commit ad9c0b369e86e75d56e229f294782a4eaf527226
Author: Alexey Bataev <a.bataev@outlook.com>
Date:   Mon Nov 18 13:49:04 2024 -0800

    [SLP]Check if the gathered loads form full vector before attempting build
it

    Need to check that the number of gathered loads in the slice forms the
    build vector to avoid compiler crash.

    Fixes #116691

